<emphasis id="5E1FED341B107A21458C8F806C77487D" italics="true">Hort. cliff. 217.</emphasis>
* 
<emphasis id="5D5A7F5C866D20517EF4EC57597AD40F" italics="true">Roy. lugdb. 283.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="609D5CC6E9C58D80C431B53DB40FD10E" pageNumber="487">
