<emphasis id="EF736CD59E7049F53D024815E7B002B6" italics="true">Dill. elth. 234. t.182. f.223.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2150CCBA6FEBE01A3C2E06F977F8DC07" pageNumber="487">
Ficoides capensis, folio lato acuto, flore albo intus luteo. 
<emphasis id="E34EB60783BD6373076B679419BE9F62" italics="true">Pet. gaz. t.78. f.10.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DA0FE0F7608B47054031B6FD153CC86C" pageNumber="487">
