<emphasis id="DBE97B628531388967981E955D362228" italics="true">Bradl. succ. 3. p.7. t.16.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BD764E5188E6392659ADCB9F935A629F" pageNumber="487">
β. Mesembr. tortuosum, foliis sempervivi congestis. 
<emphasis id="713215B60DCFD78E06DBD88D4641449E" italics="true">Dill. elth. 233. t.181. f.222.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="48C25EBFE78142A82443BC3711CCDF51" pageNumber="487">
Ficoides capensis procumbens, oleae folio, flore albo medio croceo. 
<emphasis id="7D107AB4B751E73E06319085EEC96AC7" italics="true">Bradl. succ. 2. p.7. t.16.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
